      "abstract": "This resolution proclaims May 19, 2026, as \"Until Justice Just Is Day\" in the State of Delaware and urges all Delawareans to support the mission of the YWCA\u2019s \"Until Justice Just Is\" campaign by advocating for and supporting their communities in a meaningful way."
